071,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:11:59.000Z","msg":"仆街中既仆街黎㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1a66beae88b0feab9b741d88c1e608816bcc96","tid":1852071,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工你咩都做唔到 咁小野你做到啦掛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1868584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1868584</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n推翻啲行動post 唔好俾啲失敗論上熱門<br />\n今晚極多五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c6ec2faaab97c91be051d001aacc888c1a9109","tid":1852071,"uid":300785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bee79e4ee24c2c02c6509e175bbca380d89254d0","tid":1852071,"uid":185251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:38:30.000Z","msg":"首先 係我on9可以唔洗diu我喇已經diu緊自己<br />\n<br />\n搵咗BB探熱器幾日都搵唔到 今日出到佐敦<strong>信安大藥房</strong>見到有<br />\n就心急要買啦 百靈牌耳探 HKTV MALL係賣緊$398 當然係斷晒貨啦<br />\n佢條L樣夠膽標個價 <strong>$998</strong> 佢仲話周街都無喇佢呢盒最後一盒 就算有都係呢啲價<br />\n咁我ON9信咗佢啦 事實我屋企人都真係搵咗好幾度都無 <br />\n俾完錢 見到有第2間藥房庇利金街 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">華特藥業</span></strong> 我入去8下啦 <br />\nDKLM佢賣<strong>$298</strong> 老細知我俾人昆咗叫我去嘈9佢<br />\n我去到信安叫老細退俾我 佢話貨出咗門唔退 我話一係換其他貨俾我 佢都唔肯 <br />\n連正面同我有眼神接觸都無 <br />\n呢啲正仆街個心黑色架 小朋友生意都咁L樣賺 依家都擺明係要買架啦 洗唔洗咁L閪啊<br />\n佢自己唔L戴口罩不特止 我仲見佢口罩拆開賣$68 10個 $45 5個<br />\n呢啲時勢佢咁L樣做生意 祝福佢生仔無屎忽 禍延三代<br />\n<br />\n[續集]<br />\n我再去同佢理論 好聲好氣叫佢換第2啲嘢俾我 佢唔俾仲報埋警叫我唔好走<br />\n我仲發現到佢呢頭話最後1個 轉個頭又補返兩個上架 <br />\n又講到自己做好事 講到話幫到BB買到就開心啦 大家都係唔想BB有事<br />\n炒價都算啦 仲講到自己好似好好心咁 人唔笑狗都吠 真係有咁嘅人<br />\n點知等緊狗嚟嘅時俾我發現佢賣落仔藥cytotec <span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係emergency pill啊!</span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>係真落仔藥!</strong></span><br />\n係有醫生紙都唔買得嘅藥啊 <br />\n佢仆街喇 佢仲恐嚇我 問係咪要搞到爆晒缸流晒血先安樂<br />\n俾我發現到有禁藥 就即刻話俾我換 你老味閪啦 我唔L要啦依家! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>衞生署發言人稱，非法管有或售賣醫生處方藥物均屬違法，一經定罪，最高罰款十萬元及監禁兩年。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n狗嚟到 咪俾我叫佢地搜鋪囉 條L樣仲自爆自己有閉路電視<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CUmdjG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCUmdjG3.jpg&h=5d47c425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HrZeOAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrZeOAo.jpg&h=a5aae5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2nHc13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2nHc13.jpg&h=1d89360d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cx0mtAp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCx0mtAp.jpg&h=9de38716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9x0YvOK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9x0YvOK.jpg&h=299892d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之 呢間係黑心鋪 大家唔好再去。初五快樂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"裝修期間照常營業"},{"pid":"770c1f434261bd39e75ff2d9002339cf2e644513","tid":1852071,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:38:00.000Z","msg":"推撚死佢"},{"pid":"df70594a91608c636861da68b18882c7da27ba4a","tid":1852071,"uid":277381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:45:13.000Z","msg":"9xx仲買，擺明老屈，可能屈慣大陸哩"},{"pid":"785a0d5216e6ecad1bd42ede8f157865ac788a12","tid":1852071,"uid":186608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"百靈牌耳溫槍普通藥房平時係賣緊$300，百老匯，凶澤係賣$6xx"},{"pid":"3e9204b8913ae9a7b01b019930dd53a20002d800","tid":1852071,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00121bc6151e8177dcdee0873f402ce9b946d1e3","tid":1852071,"uid":15542,"like":0,"